    "body" : "<p><a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/javase/1,5.0/docs/api/java/lang/Long.html#valueOf%28java.lang.String%29\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Long.valueOf(String s)</a> - obviously due care must be taken to protect against non-numbers if that is possible in your code.</p>\n"
