    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>It's quite simple, use\n<code>Long.valueOf(String s);</code></p>\n\n<p>For example:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>String s;\nlong l;\n\nScanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);\ns=sc.next();\nl=Long.valueOf(s);\nSystem.out.print(l);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You're done!!!</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 7499374,
      "reputation" : 435,
      "user_id" : 5698386,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/109b2939aac8b334d02b1cf6957ca012?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "Mohamed Aymen Charrada",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/5698386/mohamed-aymen-charrada"
    },
